      "content": "thanks for the info. i was worried about them clashing or something but that makes sense. since you said they hit different areas, would it be okay if i took a double dose of melatonin if the zolpidem doesn't kick in right away? like if i'm still tossing and turning after 20 mins i'll just take more melatonin to boost it? i just really need to stay asleep all night.",
