    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay i get that. i'll be careful. i'm just really stressed about how exhausted i feel during the day. if i take the zolpidem and the melatonin together, should i also take an extra dose of my allergy med (diphenhydramine) if i still feel like i can't drift off? i've heard that helps people sleep even deeper.",
